title: Japanese Meat & Potatoes

Try this with dark soy instead of soy and brown sugar.

Prep:

* 2 yellow onions, sliced
* 2 potatoes, diced
* 3 carrots, peeled and ''chopped small''
* ginger, minced
* scallions, chopped (separate)

In a large pot, brown:

* 1.5 lb ground beef

Add liquid:

* 1.5 C chicken stock
* 1/2 C mirin
* 1/4 C dark sweet soy sauce
* ~~1/4 C soy sauce~~
* ~~2 T brown sugar~~

Add veggies and simmer for 30 minutes. Top with scallions.
